title.rendered: BOSS AIR STREET CRUISER IMPRESSOR KIT

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR STREET CRUISER IMPRESSOR KIT

Boss Air Street Cruiser Impressor Kit available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

This kit is a great starter air package kit for a 2 airbag system, onboard air for the 4×4 or running air lockers. Featuring Boss Air’s PX06 12volt 1.8cfm 100% Duty Cycle Air Compressor for rapid refilling the 5 port tank ready for the next use.

Also included is Boss Air’s light weight, no rust Aluminium 3 gallon air tank, heat treated, shot blasted and anodised.

Includes;

  • 1 x PX-06 12volt 100% Duty, 1.8cfm Air Compressors
  • 1 x AT-03  5 port Boss Aluminium Air Tank
  • 1 x 110-135psi Pressure Switch
  • 1 x Check Valves
  • 1 x Braided Hoses
  • 1 x Brass 1/4″ Bung
  • 1 x Drain Tap
  • 1 x 40amp Relay
  • Instruction Sheet
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
